  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes
  sourcePage 3
obj_root_law_sections_3_content:
  string
  line 3
  line `SCHEDULE A.`
  line `Form of Commission to be used to a holder of alienated Revenue or his Agent for`
  line `enabling him to recover such Revenue`
  line `The Governor in Council of Bombay by virtue of the powers vested in him by Act XIII, of 1842,`
  line `is pleased to confer on you -------------- -------------- (Jageerdar, & c., or Agent, & c., as the case may be)`
  line `power to realize all Revenue demands due to you (or to your principal) from the Villages and Lands`
  line `specified in this Com mission in the manner prescr ibed in ( or in Sections ---- ------------- of) this Act.`
  line `The Villages and Lands over which the power thus conferred upon you extends are as follows:`
  line `(Here enter the description.)`
  line `The within delegated power is vested in you during the pleasure and subject to the re - call of the`
  line `said Governor in Council.`
  line `_____ __________`
  line SEAL
obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes:
  string
  line
